OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1778137535
OL,3,CPolice major crime team probe
OL,4,C'suspicious' death of man found in
OL,5,Croof garden
OL,7,FAvon and Somerset Police say their
OL,8,Fmajor crime team is investigating the
OL,9,Fdeath of a man found in a roof garden
OL,10,Fat a block of flats in Bristol.
OL,12,FOfficers were called at 8.19am on
OL,13,FTuesday (5 May) to attend the scene in
OL,14,FRedcliff Street after the discovery
OL,15,Fwas made by a member of the public.
OL,17,FPolice say they are currently treating
OL,18,Fthe man's death as suspicious and a
OL,19,Fforensic post-mortem examination is
OL,20,Fdue to take place today to determine
OL,21,Fhow he died.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
