FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1778137535
OL,3,CPolice major crime team probe
OL,4,C'suspicious' death of man found in
OL,5,Croof garden
OL,7,FFormal identification has not yet been
OL,8,Fcarried out, but they believe that he
OL,9,Fwas in his 50s.
OL,11,FPolice say his next of kin have been
OL,12,Fspoken to and they will be supported
OL,13,Fby specially trained family liaison
OL,14,Fofficers.
OL,16,FPolice are continuing to speak to
OL,17,Fresidents and will be carrying out
OL,18,Fsearches in the area, as well as
OL,19,Ffurther forensic enquiries and a full
OL,20,Freview of all available CCTV and other
OL,21,Ffootage.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
