OL,3,CPolice major crime team probe
OL,4,C'suspicious' death of man found in
OL,5,Croof garden
OL,7,FSuperintendent Matt Ebbs said: "The
OL,8,Ffamily of the deceased have been
OL,9,Fupdated and we'll be providing them
OL,10,Fwith any support they need at this
OL,11,Fextremely distressing time.
OL,13,F"The man's death is being treated as
OL,14,Fsuspicious and a full and thorough
OL,15,Finvestigation is well underway.
OL,26,@oD@`OUuD@AOU
